Decorator that registera task generator method which will be executed
before the functions of given name(s):

```
from waflib.TaskGen import feature, before
@feature('myfeature')
@before_method('fun2')
def fun1(self):
        print('feature 1!')
@feature('myfeature')
def fun2(self):
        print('feature 2!')
def build(bld):
        bld(features='myfeature')
